    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Luminescence dating technique which, by using a lamp or laser, measures the stored energy in the form of light which is trapped in minerals. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047747/Gibbons, Spectacular Dates, Science (1997)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047745/Aitken and Valladas, Luminescence Dating, Philosophical Transactions (1992)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Luminescencia que fecha la técnica usando una lámpara o un laser, mide la energía almacenada bajo la forma de luz que es atrapada en minerales.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Luminescentiedateringstechniek op basis van meting, door gebruik van een lamp of laser, van de hoeveelheid energie die in de vorm van licht in mineralen is opgeslagen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
